FT  08 OCT 93 / UK Company News: TJ Hughes lower after poor summer
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
TJ HUGHES, the USM-quoted multiple discount store group, reported a 19 per
cent fall in profits before tax in its unseasonal first half to July 31.
