FT  07 OCT 93 / UK Company News: Shepherd Neame rises 15%
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
DESPITE discounting by competitors, Shepherd Neame, the independent
Kent-based brewer, lifted pre-tax profits by 15.5 per cent over the 12
months to June 26.
